# <%= current_page.data.title %>

This is the preferred DR path for ease, speed, consistency and auditability.

## Scope

- CNP restore automation
- CPP restore automation
- Target region: UK South

## Information required before running the pipeline

- Source Postgresql details required:
  - subscription Id
  - resource group
  - server name
- Storage account details required:
  - CNP: **cnpvaultrestorationprod**
  - CPP Live: **sacppvaultrestoreprd**
- Backup Vault details required:
  - CNP:
    - subscription: **8999dec3-0104-4a27-94ee-6588559729d1**
    - resource group: **mgmt-infra-prod-rg**
    - name: **cnp-backup-vault**
  - CNP Live:
    - subscription: **9ab65d81-930d-4cc0-a93d-367e14676bc0**
    - resource group: **cpp-infra-prd**
    - name: **cpp-backup-vault**
- Restore Point Id:
  - If restoring a specific point in time the Id of the restore point is required
  - If restoring latest available this will be automatically discovered

